App Privacy Policy
Thank you very much for downloading the Mouse Link application (hereinafter referred to as the App). In order to allow you to use the various services and information of this App with peace of mind, we hereby explain to you the privacy protection policy of this App to protect your rights and interests. Please Please read the following content in detail:
Scope of application of privacy protection policy
Privacy protection policy content, including how this App handles personally identifiable information collected when you use App services. The privacy protection policy does not apply to related linked websites outside this App, nor does it apply to people who are not entrusted by or involved in the management of this App.
How personal data is collected, processed and used
When you use this App, we may collect the following types of information:
Usage information : We may collect information about your use of the App, including your device model, operating system version, IP address, App usage, etc.
This App will retain the name, email address, contact information, usage time, etc. you provide when you use interactive functions such as service mailboxes and questionnaires.
We may use the information we collect to:
Provide, maintain and improve the App
Provide you with a customized experience
To contact you, provide customer support and respond to your inquiries and feedback
Enforce our Terms of Use and Privacy Policy
Data protection
This App host is equipped with various information security equipment and necessary security measures such as firewalls and anti-virus systems. Strict protection measures are adopted to protect the application and your personal data. Only authorized personnel can access your data. All personnel handling personal data have signed confidentiality contracts. Anyone who violates confidentiality obligations will be subject to relevant legal sanctions.
If it is necessary to entrust other units to provide services due to business needs, the App will also strictly require them to comply with confidentiality obligations and take necessary inspection procedures to ensure that they will indeed comply.
This App completely uses the development environment and platform tools provided by Google and Microsoft, and does not use third-party resources at all.
Relevant links external to the application
This App provides Internet links to other websites. You can also click to enter other websites through the links provided by this App. However, the privacy protection policy of this linked website does not apply to this App. You must refer to the privacy protection policy of the linked website.
Policy on Sharing Personal Information with Third Parties
This App will never provide, exchange, rent or sell any of your personal information to other individuals, groups, private enterprises or public agencies, except where there is a legal basis or contractual obligation.
The situations subject to the proviso in the preceding paragraph include, but are not limited to:
With your written consent.
The law clearly stipulates this.
To avoid danger to your life, body, liberty or property.
Cooperation with public agencies or academic research institutions is necessary for statistical or academic research based on public interest, and the data has been processed or collected by the provider so that the specific parties cannot be identified based on the method of disclosure.
When your behavior in the App violates the terms of service or may damage or hinder the rights of the App and other users or cause harm to anyone, your personal information will be disclosed after analysis by the App management unit for the purpose of identifying, contacting or taking legal action. What is necessary.
Benefit your interests.
When this App entrusts manufacturers to assist in collecting, processing or using your personal information, it will fully supervise and manage the outsourced manufacturers or individuals.
Privacy rights
Subject to applicable privacy laws, you may have the right to access, correct, delete or restrict our processing of your personal information. If you wish to exercise these rights or have any privacy questions or concerns, please contact us using the contact information provided below.
Amendments to the Privacy Policy
This App Privacy Protection Policy will be revised at any time in response to needs, and the revised terms will be posted on the website.
